{"tid":2315001,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"28歲的迷惘，前路點揀？","createTime":"2020-12-07T02:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T05:43:51.000Z","uid":35361,"like":3,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7e0a31ab93dae771146b1253c54a114147eee180","tid":2315001,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T02:20:24.000Z","msg":"我非5大bba畢業，一畢業非常幸福地有屋企人幫手，去左爸爸朋友公司做，而且個價絕非fg價同埋同事好肯教，真真正正袋住糧學野<br />\n<br />\n之後做左2年就轉工，之後份都係做左2年又走，依家做緊果份就準備踏入第3年<br />\n<br />\n多得第一份工既「幫助」，我做野第3年已經做緊AM，依家做緊M 都叫逗緊40k有多<br />\n<br />\n但係工作真係越嚟越忙，我又搬左出去，完全無乜時間返屋企，可能因為呢個關係...爸爸最近同我食左餐飯講....<br />\n<br />\n我依有2條路...<br />\n一係繼續出面打拼，但會失去時間倍家人<br />\n<br />\n一係就爸爸話...佢本身手上好多物業收租，佢唔會俾我打理，我亦唔識打理<br />\n但會俾出面人管理，然後成立信托基金，每個月出糧俾我，條件係我要轉份輕鬆既文員工，搬返返去屋企住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我好想多時間倍屋企人，但又唔想咁後生做「兒子」。我覺得我仲有得上位..."},{"pid":"2f16e536be270c722caf72e559a0521977e5ab85","tid":2315001,"uid":12628,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T02:21:44.000Z","msg":"哥哥，我幫你繼承左爸爸啲物業佢啦。你走啦，唔使返黎"},{"pid":"31849b51e62667614615b66e2f09b6c2974f9664","tid":2315001,"uid":152244,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T02:23:15.000Z","msg":"呢d煩惱就唔好開po啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 14k文員"},{"pid":"8ad42ae5624d4311718ab20c68959276d54912d1","tid":2315001,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2f16e536be270c722caf72e559a0521977e5ab85","tid":2315001,"uid":12628,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"